description	"OOM-Series Pilot Battle Droid

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (2)

^8Attributes:
- Auto-Repair System (Heal) (1)
- View Ally Stats

^3Abilities:
- Repair Others [Hold Use on Allies]
- Supply Ammunition [Hold Use on Allies]

These droids were programmed to pilot all vehicles and vessels used by the droid forces, but were also deployed in space battles to man turrets, carry ammunition, and monitor the decks and hangars for breaches and boarding parties. "